  </p><article itemscope="" data-type-id="1100" data-guid="1100-6531433">

            
            
  


        

  


        
        
              <section>

                  
          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>RadioShack is back from the grave. After going bankrupt in 2017, the brand was acquired by new owners in 2023, and the company is using its new lease on life to offer the usual assortment of electronics along with a cool lineup of new <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=RadioShack+Revived+From+The+Dead%2C+Releases+Retro+Audio+Gear&amp;fnauthor=brendanhesse&amp;fndate=2025-05-12+11%3A59%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-05-12+12%3A00%3A00&amp;fnarticle_id=6531433&amp;fntype1=Tech&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.radioshack.com%2Fvintage%3Fhid%3Dmmb-esc27&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fradioshack-revived-from-the-dead-releases-retro-audio-gear%2F1100-6531433%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">vintage -style audio gear</a>. Retro speakers, radios, and turntables are all included in the new RadioShack catalog, many of which are already receiving generous discounts.</p><p>The <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=RadioShack+Revived+From+The+Dead%2C+Releases+Retro+Audio+Gear&amp;fnauthor=brendanhesse&amp;fndate=2025-05-12+11%3A59%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-05-12+12%3A00%3A00&amp;fnarticle_id=6531433&amp;fntype1=Tech&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.radioshack.com%2Fradioshack-vintage-turntable-with-bluetooth-and-fm-radio-4001791%2Fp&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fradioshack-revived-from-the-dead-releases-retro-audio-gear%2F1100-6531433%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Vintage Turntable with Bluetooth and FM Radio</a> is the most premium at $126 (was $140). Along with a chance to play your favorite vinyls (and support for three speeds and auto return), the turntable features a built-in AM/FM radio, support for CDs, a cassette player, and the ability to record audio directly to a connected USB or SD card. It’s all housed inside an engineered wood cabinet with a rich brown color and retro brass accents.</p><figure data-align="center" data-size="large" data-img-src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1702/17023653/4491266-aff22481201a04065263760e3d4ee0f9.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4491266" data-ratio="0.636" data-width="2000" data-embed-type="image"><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1702/17023653/4491266-aff22481201a04065263760e3d4ee0f9.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4491266"></a><figcaption>Vintage Turntable</figcaption><img src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1702/17023653/4491266-aff22481201a04065263760e3d4ee0f9.jpg"></figure><figure data-embed-type="gallery" data-img-src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1702/17023653/4491267-4001790_1.png,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1702/17023653/4491269-1202267_1.png,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1702/17023653/4491270-1202268.png,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1702/17023653/4491271-4001973_1.png,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1702/17023653/4491272-4001974_1.png" data-ref-id="1300-4491267,1300-4491269,1300-4491270,1300-4491271,1300-4491272" data-resize-urls="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/square_avatar/1702/17023653/4491267-4001790_1.png,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/square_avatar/1702/17023653/4491269-1202267_1.png,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/square_avatar/1702/17023653/4491270-1202268.png,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/square_avatar/1702/17023653/4491271-4001973_1.png,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/square_avatar/1702/17023653/4491272-4001974_1.png"><p>Gallery</p>     <img src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1702/17023653/4491267-4001790_1.png,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1702/17023653/4491269-1202267_1.png,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1702/17023653/4491270-1202268.png,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1702/17023653/4491271-4001973_1.png,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1702/17023653/4491272-4001974_1.png"></figure><p>A more affordable alternative is the <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=RadioShack+Revived+From+The+Dead%2C+Releases+Retro+Audio+Gear&amp;fnauthor=brendanhesse&amp;fndate=2025-05-12+11%3A59%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-05-12+12%3A00%3A00&amp;fnarticle_id=6531433&amp;fntype1=Tech&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.radioshack.com%2Fradioshack-portable-suitcase-turntable-with-bluetooth-4001790%2Fp&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fradioshack-revived-from-the-dead-releases-retro-audio-gear%2F1100-6531433%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Portable Suitcase Turntable with Bluetooth</a>. It’s on sale for $72 (was $80), and its slim footprint makes it a great option if you often travel with your favorite records.</p><p>RadioShack is offering a handful of retro radios, too. The <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=RadioShack+Revived+From+The+Dead%2C+Releases+Retro+Audio+Gear&amp;fnauthor=brendanhesse&amp;fndate=2025-05-12+11%3A59%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-05-12+12%3A00%3A00&amp;fnarticle_id=6531433&amp;fntype1=Tech&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.radioshack.com%2Fradioshack-am-fm-sw-3-band-vintage-radio-with-bluetooth-function-and-usb-tf-ports-white-1202268%2Fp&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fradioshack-revived-from-the-dead-releases-retro-audio-gear%2F1100-6531433%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">3-Band Vintage Radio</a> comes with Bluetooth support and the ability to play MP3 files from a USB port, while the <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=RadioShack+Revived+From+The+Dead%2C+Releases+Retro+Audio+Gear&amp;fnauthor=brendanhesse&amp;fndate=2025-05-12+11%3A59%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-05-12+12%3A00%3A00&amp;fnarticle_id=6531433&amp;fntype1=Tech&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.radioshack.com%2Fradioshack-am-fm-2-band-vintage-radio-with-bluetooth-function-and-usb-tf-ports-white-1202267%2Fp&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fradioshack-revived-from-the-dead-releases-retro-audio-gear%2F1100-6531433%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">2-Band Vintage Radio</a> boasts a vibrant LED display and the same Bluetooth support. The 3-Band Radio is $25 while the 2-Band is $40.</p><p>Rounding out the new catalog are two new speakers. One is a sizable <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=RadioShack+Revived+From+The+Dead%2C+Releases+Retro+Audio+Gear&amp;fnauthor=brendanhesse&amp;fndate=2025-05-12+11%3A59%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-05-12+12%3A00%3A00&amp;fnarticle_id=6531433&amp;fntype1=Tech&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.radioshack.com%2Fradioshack-retro-style-bluethooth-speaker-with-fm-radio-4001974%2Fp&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fradioshack-revived-from-the-dead-releases-retro-audio-gear%2F1100-6531433%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">240W Retro Bluetooth Speaker with FM Radio</a>, featuring a premium leather body and minimalist metal grill. It’s on sale for $104 (was $130), so give it a look if you want to bring a nostalgic piece of gear into your home. The other is a smaller <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=RadioShack+Revived+From+The+Dead%2C+Releases+Retro+Audio+Gear&amp;fnauthor=brendanhesse&amp;fndate=2025-05-12+11%3A59%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-05-12+12%3A00%3A00&amp;fnarticle_id=6531433&amp;fntype1=Tech&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.radioshack.com%2Fradioshack-bluetooth-retro-speaker-with-microphone-input-4001973%2Fp&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fradioshack-revived-from-the-dead-releases-retro-audio-gear%2F1100-6531433%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">80W Retro Speaker</a>. It uses the same high-grade leather and metal construction, though it’s combination of rose gold and black makes it a bit more stylish. It’s also cheaper at $80 (was $100).</p><p>It's unclear how long all of these discounts will stick around, so cash in on the deals while you can.</p><h2>RadioShack Retro Collection</h2><ul><li><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=RadioShack+Revived+From+The+Dead%2C+Releases+Retro+Audio+Gear&amp;fnauthor=brendanhesse&amp;fndate=2025-05-12+11%3A59%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-05-12+12%3A00%3A00&amp;fnarticle_id=6531433&amp;fntype1=Tech&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.radioshack.com%2Fradioshack-am-fm-sw-3-band-vintage-radio-with-bluetooth-function-and-usb-tf-ports-white-1202268%2Fp&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fradioshack-revived-from-the-dead-releases-retro-audio-gear%2F1100-6531433%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">3-Band Vintage Radio</a> -- $25</li><li><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=RadioShack+Revived+From+The+